    effortless-ntwf:title "Identity-conditioned explained theorem: all unexplained sign-flips confined to contested-org-choice and collider-proxy identities" ;
    effortless-ntwf:evidence "Loop-85 at N=238: H-unexplained-flips-only-nonconfounders PASS. UnexplainedConfounderSignFlipCount=0. The three unexplained flips (conc-29 exception list) map exclusively to id-contested-org-choice (2) and id-collider-proxy (1). This extends the loop-74 biconditional (conc-29): explained↔confounder holds for every unambiguous confounder identity; violations are confined to ontologically ambiguous categories. inv-unexplained-identity-sink: PASS (critical, 30 total invariants)." ;
    effortless-ntwf:witnessedInLoop "loop-85" ;
    effortless-ntwf:targetLoop "loop-85" ;
    effortless-ntwf:traditionId "tradition-dag" .

effortless-ntwf:conc-36-perfect-balance-theorem a effortless-ntwf:Conclusions ;
    effortless-ntwf:conclusionId "conc-36-perfect-balance-theorem" ;
    effortless-ntwf:category "corpus-theorem" ;
    effortless-ntwf:status "witnessed" ;
    effortless-ntwf:reportTier "critical" ;
    effortless-ntwf:validatingHypothesis "H-perfect-balance-sufficient-safety" ;
    effortless-ntwf:title "Perfect allocation balance is a sufficient condition for no manifest Simpson's Paradox" ;
    effortless-ntwf:evidence "Loop-86: inv-perfect-balance-no-flip PASS 118/118. All 118 TreatmentRankings with ArmSizeRatio=0.5 AND MaxStratumImbalance=0.0 have IsSignFlip=FALSE across all 8 domains and 19 confounder archetypes. Minimum imbalance at any sign-flip study: 0.033 (flu-vaccine-elderly-mortality, demographic-composition). Safety corridor [0.0, 0.033) contains zero sign-flips. This is a sufficient-condition theorem: perfect balance guarantees no manifest paradox, domain-agnostically." ;
    effortless-ntwf:witnessedInLoop "loop-86" ;
    effortless-ntwf:targetLoop "loop-86" ;
    effortless-ntwf:traditionId "tradition-dag" .

effortless-ntwf:conc-37-purity-inversion-theorem a effortless-ntwf:Conclusions ;
    effortless-ntwf:conclusionId "conc-37-purity-inversion-theorem" ;
    effortless-ntwf:category "corpus-theorem" ;
    effortless-ntwf:status "witnessed" ;
    effortless-ntwf:reportTier "critical" ;
    effortless-ntwf:validatingHypothesis "H-purity-inversion" ;
    effortless-ntwf:title "Purity inversion: high SignalPurity anti-predicts safe stratification — collider geometry maximizes it" ;
    effortless-ntwf:evidence "Loop-87: collider/selection mean SignalPurity=0.916 (n=12); selection/frailty mean SignalPurity=1.000 (n=5) — the two mechanism classes that must NOT be stratified have the highest purity in the corpus. Demographic-composition (stratify-appropriate) mean SignalPurity=0.624 (n=35). inv-collider-purity-dominance PASS. H-purity-inversion confirmed. PurityTrapFlag encodes the trap for direct query. Researchers using data cleanliness as a quality heuristic will systematically misidentify collider/selection studies as safe-to-stratify — the instrument makes this error visible." ;
    effortless-ntwf:witnessedInLoop "loop-87" ;
    effortless-ntwf:targetLoop "loop-87" ;
    effortless-ntwf:traditionId "tradition-dag" .

