effortless-ntwf:loop-46 a effortless-ntwf:Loops ;
    effortless-ntwf:loopId "loop-46" ;
    effortless-ntwf:title "Rulespeak regen + loop table cleanup: five-type taxonomy in human-readable narrative" ;
    effortless-ntwf:status "complete" ;
    effortless-ntwf:newConcept "Rulespeak narrative update" ;
    effortless-ntwf:domainQuestion "Does the rulespeak narrative accurately describe the five-type taxonomy (A, B, C+, C-, D) and the InstrumentScore screening formula?" ;
    effortless-ntwf:mockDataNote "Rulespeak narrative regenerated. Five-type taxonomy (A/B/C+/C-/D), SignalPurity theorem, AllocationDirection, InstrumentScore, ScreeningTier, and ScreeningVerdict all appear in the narrative. Loop table updated: loops 36-46 all complete. All 17 invariants pass. AvgSignalPurity across corpus ≈ 0.533." ;
    effortless-ntwf:nextSuggestion "Scale path: ingest additional published studies (target 50+) to test whether SignalPurity correlates with domain, causal role, or sample size at statistical significance." ;
