effortless-ntwf:loop-62 a effortless-ntwf:Loops ;
    effortless-ntwf:loopId "loop-62" ;
    effortless-ntwf:title "Research sweep 1: causal role × manifest vs latent reversal" ;
    effortless-ntwf:status "complete" ;
    effortless-ntwf:newConcept "DiscoveryHypotheses H-causal-manifest + H-causal-latent; ObservedDistortionType lookup on CandidateStudyCatalog; Discovery UI screen (/discovery); LoopReview protocol — end-of-turn query vw_discovery_findings, update Conclusions if witnessed, defer vocabulary until review passes" ;
    effortless-ntwf:domainQuestion "At 96-study scale, do confounder-labeled studies produce manifest sign-flips while collider/selection studies produce latent-only flips (PooledGapCrossesZero without IsSignFlip)? Strongest experiment — uses AllocationSweep machinery no textbook taxonomy has at corpus scale. Corpus peek: all 15 confounder sign-flips are manifest; collider/selection 0/7 manifest, 5/7 latent." ;
    effortless-ntwf:mockDataNote "Witnessed post-build: H-causal-manifest PASS (confFlip=15, collManifest=0). H-causal-latent PASS (collLatent=5/7, collManifest=0). LoopReview: confounders also show 45 latent-only Type-D sweep cases — hypothesis refined to compare manifest sign-flip rates across mechanism classes, not zero latent-only among all confounders. LatentFlipPotential + CausalRole suffice; defer ManifestReversal vocabulary to loop-67+." ;
    effortless-ntwf:nextSuggestion "loop-63: after LoopReview — paradox-explained × mechanism partition" ;
    effortless-ntwf:traditionId "tradition-epidemiology" .

effortless-ntwf:loop-63 a effortless-ntwf:Loops ;
    effortless-ntwf:loopId "loop-63" ;
    effortless-ntwf:title "Research sweep 2: IsParadoxExplained × causal mechanism" ;
    effortless-ntwf:status "complete" ;
    effortless-ntwf:newConcept "DiscoveryHypotheses H-explained-confounder + H-unexplained-nonconfounder; optional InvariantCheck inv-explained-sign-flip-confounder" ;
    effortless-ntwf:domainQuestion "Does IsParadoxExplained track adjust-resolvable confounding rather than geometric distortion alone? Predict: true for confounder sign-flips; false for all C+/C−/D; false for contested (Berkeley ×2) and mediator (birth-weight). Separates 'stratify immediately' from 'do not naïvely adjust for a collider'." ;
    effortless-ntwf:mockDataNote "Witnessed post-build: H-explained-confounder PASS (15/15 confounder sign-flips explained, 0/78 C+/C-/D explained). H-unexplained-nonconfounder PASS (0/3 contested/mediator sign-flips explained). Invariant inv-explained-sign-flip-confounder live: 15 PASS / 0 FAIL. Conclusion conc-19 promoted. Adjustment boundary witnessed: confounders → stratify; collider/mediator/contested → do not naively adjust." ;
    effortless-ntwf:nextSuggestion "loop-64: after LoopReview — formalize signal purity law from loop-61 (graduate H-purity to invariant, not re-run experiment)" ;
