    effortless-ntwf:relationToHannanPearl "Methodologically distinct from Pearl: SGS uses constraint-based structure discovery from conditional independence tests; Pearl uses do-calculus and interventional logic. Both treat the paradox as a confounding problem but differ in how to identify confounders from data." ;
