    effortless-ntwf:relationToHannanPearl "Collaborated with Pearl (Greenland, Robins & Pearl 1999, Statistical Science) on confounding and collapsibility. Greenland operationalises the paradox for epidemiological practice where Pearl's do-calculus is abstract." ;
