    effortless-ntwf:mechanismNote "Strata are exactly equal size (StratumFraction=0.5/0.5) but allocation within each stratum is skewed oppositely, producing a manifest sign-flip purely from within-stratum imbalance — demonstrates the SignalPurity theorem does not require stratum-size imbalance, only allocation imbalance." ;
    effortless-ntwf:conditioningRisk "confounder" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitHash "08f3b8eca267a7dae0c83bf207bcde3bceb0fde7" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitDate "2026-07-08" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitSubject "Completed Loops 86-89 - Add new candidate datasets and studies for Simpson's Paradox analysis" ;
    effortless-ntwf:causalRoleEverRevised false .

effortless-ntwf:zero-corrected-gap-boundary-allocation-manufactured-signal a effortless-ntwf:StratumVariables ;
    effortless-ntwf:stratumVariableId "zero-corrected-gap-boundary-allocation-manufactured-signal" ;
    effortless-ntwf:study effortless-ntwf:zero-corrected-gap-boundary ;
    effortless-ntwf:variableName "allocation-manufactured-signal" ;
    effortless-ntwf:causalRole "confounder" ;
    effortless-ntwf:affectsTreatmentAssignment true ;
    effortless-ntwf:affectsOutcome true ;
    effortless-ntwf:mechanismNote "Allocation imbalance manufactures the entire observed pooled gap (5.4pp) from a true corrected effect of exactly zero (CorrectedGap=0.0, SignalPurity=0.0) — the purest form of allocation artifact in the corpus, useful as the SignalPurity lower-bound anchor (purity=0 means 100% of observed signal is allocation, 0% true effect)." ;
    effortless-ntwf:conditioningRisk "confounder" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitHash "08f3b8eca267a7dae0c83bf207bcde3bceb0fde7" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitDate "2026-07-08" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitSubject "Completed Loops 86-89 - Add new candidate datasets and studies for Simpson's Paradox analysis" ;
    effortless-ntwf:causalRoleEverRevised false .

effortless-ntwf:collider-purity-boundary-flip-near-independent-stratification a effortless-ntwf:StratumVariables ;
    effortless-ntwf:stratumVariableId "collider-purity-boundary-flip-near-independent-stratification" ;
    effortless-ntwf:study effortless-ntwf:collider-purity-boundary-flip ;
    effortless-ntwf:variableName "near-independent-stratification" ;
    effortless-ntwf:causalRole "collider" ;
    effortless-ntwf:affectsTreatmentAssignment true ;
    effortless-ntwf:affectsOutcome true ;
    effortless-ntwf:mechanismNote "Constructed via 1.2M-trial adversarial search for the highest-SignalPurity configuration that still produces a manifest sign-flip. Best found: purity=0.49994, asymptotically approaching but never reaching the 0.5 theorem boundary (conc-20). Tagged collider (not confounder) to probe conc-30 (collider-no-manifest theorem) at its tightest empirically-discoverable edge — the geometry structurally resists high-purity flips even under adversarial search, not merely by absence in the observed real-data corpus." ;
    effortless-ntwf:conditioningRisk "collider" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitHash "08f3b8eca267a7dae0c83bf207bcde3bceb0fde7" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitDate "2026-07-08" ;
    effortless-ntwf:annotationCommitSubject "Completed Loops 86-89 - Add new candidate datasets and studies for Simpson's Paradox analysis" ;
    effortless-ntwf:causalRoleEverRevised false .

